    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1770464403\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1770464403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1770464403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>This game is an independent work inspired by American urban legends and is not affiliated with any TV series, movies, or copyrighted fictional universes.<br><br>All characters, events and coincidences that may occur during the game are purely coincidental and have no relation to real people, places or events. Any coincidences with real situations, personalities or historical facts are purely coincidental. The content and plot of the game are fictional and created for entertainment purposes only. The developers are not responsible for possible misinterpretations or unintended consequences of game events. <br>Play at your own discretion and exercise good judgment in all things.</i><br><br>The main character, Sim, has a wife who goes missing. During the investigation, he learns that she is in the hands of a powerful demon who is blackmailing our protagonist in every way possible.<br>He enlists the help of his best friend Dan, who also has a personal grudge against the demon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/680809f3295c03ed5e364fc97bd74d67.poster.avif?t=1770464403\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/680809f3295c03ed5e364fc97bd74d67.webm?t=1770464403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/680809f3295c03ed5e364fc97bd74d67.mp4?t=1770464403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>They will have to put a lot of effort to get out of this difficult situation.<br><br>When they start actively searching for the main suspect, the danger on their way grows to unbelievable proportions. The police and the hunters of unclean powers think that the same man is behind all these crimes...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monsters</h2>.Along the way, we will encounter all kinds and horrible monsters that we will have to fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/c4aa1ea4404a311295a25984a243fdb6.poster.avif?t=1770464403\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/c4aa1ea4404a311295a25984a243fdb6.webm?t=1770464403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210000/extras/c4aa1ea4404a311295a25984a243fdb6.mp4?t=1770464403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fear and Terror</h2>.Evil awaits them in every home, every village, and every forest.",
